{"tid":1906483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港標準及檢定中心對蔣麗芸議員的口罩測試出左聲明","createTime":"2020-03-02T03:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T14:54:13.000Z","uid":22556,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7d616c8cccc931125ac4b786e079548e7ee186e9","tid":1906483,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:33:16.000Z","msg":"【聲明】<br />\n<br />\n二零二零年二月六日，一位市民提供了一些口罩樣本委託本中心進行「微粒子過濾效率」(Particulate Filtration Efficiency, PFE) 測試。要求本中心將樣本分成二部分，一部分樣本不做任何處理，而將另一部分樣本放置在攝氏一百度下蒸十分鐘，對兩部分口罩的微粒子過濾效率 (PFE) 進行測試，分別記錄數據。本中心就客人送來之樣本進行以上測試及發出報告。<br />\n <br />\n現時市場上口罩大多是根據美國 ASTM F2100 標準，該標準要求評價一次性外科口罩是否符合規格，需要通過以下的測試內容：<br />\n <br />\n1.  細菌過濾效率測試 (Bacterial Filtration Efficiency (BFE)%);<br />\n2.  微粒子過濾效率測試 (Particulate Filtration Efficiency (PFE)%);<br />\n3.  壓差測試 (Differential Pressure (Delta P) mm H2O/cm&sup2;);<br />\n4.  合成血液穿透性測試 (Resistance of Penetration by Synthetic Blood, mmHg);<br />\n5.  可燃性測試 (Flammability test to Class 1.)<br />\n <br />\n微粒子過濾效率測試 (PFE) 是判斷該口罩是否有效過濾微粒子例如塵埃，是安全標準的眾多測試要求中的其中一個內容要求。<br />\n <br />\n註：本次測試報告只涉及提交的樣本，且僅提供測試數據而沒有作出任何結論。<br />\n<br />\n#STC #香港標準及檢定中心 #聲明 #口罩測試<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/106348029411673/posts/2895164117196703/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F106348029411673%2Fposts%2F2895164117196703%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=08c25179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/106348029411673/posts/2895164117196703/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"ae2174df62cc752bb76bed0a650881a4ab129842","tid":1906483,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"驚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9345006ff25c7fccf451e4f0601cb978fbfc5e3","tid":1906483,"uid":84128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:34:35.000Z","msg":"戴哂頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a22a42dec49f4b174faf9fdc5bcbd3d44cde8d5","tid":1906483,"uid":46906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:35:04.000Z","msg":"光速割蓆"},{"pid":"05cc8ac1ae3a337fd4f7d878ba4756b8fea780de","tid":1906483,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d68ad71a4c62e43fd36f853b03d1564d0fb070e","tid":1906483,"uid":170294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"正常 你比我蒸完的口罩做過濾test<br />\n<br />\n一陣有人蒸用完中蕉 依間野就食得屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007afb1806f03e19babc28d5815e690a7c2cf149","tid":1906483,"uid":261332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:36:39.000Z","msg":"吓，咁個報告呢？唔見嘅？"},{"pid":"671c4f9560866217f263c06e3ac9128d0fcd63dc","tid":1906483,"uid":128594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"估到元秋剩係攞個data 就自己亂吹<br />\n<br />\n公證行如果自己唔出聲就真係唔使旨意有公信力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b98ba477bb149f179b24fb2d3b31c907e07e3cd","tid":1906483,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"嗰兩份樣本係芸e自己話一個蒸過一個冇蒸<br />\n唔係測試中心自己蒸<br />\n完全冇control"},{"pid":"5e034a6557cde2b4cdef23a853deac505ff163fd","tid":1906483,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"不如驗下有冇病毒仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a7197bcd45767231175284cbfac6aa501da0a